iption%20of%20barcode%20formats%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22isbn.html%22%3EAbout%20ISBN%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%20(for%20books%20and%20other%20media)%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdanfuzz%2Fbarcode-server%22%3ESource%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3EInspiration%20and%20History%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20This%20toy%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20October%202%2C%201994%20edition%20of%20%3Ccite%3EYou%20Can%20With%0A%20%20Beakman%20and%20Jax%3C%2Fcite%3E%20(a%20newspaper%20comic)%2C%20which%20featured%20an%20excellent%0A%20%20description%20of%20how%20UPC%20barcodes%20work.%20Running%20near-continuously%20since%20that%0A%20%20fateful%20day%20in%20the%20fall%20of%201994%2C%20this%20was%20the%20first%20barcode%20generating%20site%20on%0A%20%20the%20web%2C%20and%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20public%20websites%20(if%20not%20%3Ci%3Ethe%3C%2Fi%3E%0A%20%20first%20such%20website)%20to%20serve%20instantly-generated%20images.%20At%20first%2C%20the%20server%0A%20%20only%20did%20the%20original%20UPC-A%20form%20(the%20most%20common%20product%20barcode%20type%20in%20the%0A%20%20USA%20at%20the%20time)%2C%20but%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202001%2C%20improvements%20were%20made%20such%20that%0A%20%20the%20server%20could%20produce%20pretty%20much%20any%20commonly-used%20UPC%20or%20EAN%20barcode.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20Things%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%20sometime%20around%202010%2C%20when%20%22XBM%22%20(the%20image%0A%20%20format%20produced%20by%20the%20server)%20stopped%20being%20supported%20by%20most%20web%20browsers.%0A%20%20At%20that%20point%2C%20the%20server%20continued%20to%20work%20%E2%80%94%20sorta%20%E2%80%94%20except%20that%0A%20%20it%20wasn't%20really%20easy%20to%20actually%20see%20what%20it%20was%20producing.%20Then%2C%20in%202023%2C%0A%20%20the%20whole%20website%20was%20moved%20to%20a%20new%20system%20which%20didn't%20support%20%22CGI%22%20(the%0A%20%20very%20basic%20web%20application%20framework%20that%20the%20Barcode%20Server%20used)%2C%20and%20that%0A%20%20totally%20broke%20it.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20Finally%2C%20again%20in%202023%2C%20the%20entire%20codebase%20of%20the%20server%20was%20revamped%2C%20such%0A%20%20that%20it%20once%20again%20operates%E2%80%A6%20and%20even%20better%20that%20it%20did%20in%20the%20first%0A%20%20place!%20Instead%20of%20being%20a%20back-end%20server%20written%20in%20C%20and%20glued%20together%20with%0A%20%20shell%20scripts%2C%20it%20is%20now%20a%20front-end%20browser%20application.%20So%2C%20perhaps%0A%20%20technically%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20really%20a%20%22server%22%20so%20much%20as%20a%20fancy%20web%20page.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3EOfficial%20Barcode%20Numbers%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20Sometimes%20people%20end%20up%20here%20because%20they're%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20how%20to%0A%20%20get%20a%20UPC%20code%20assigned%20for%20a%20product%20they%20wish%20to%20sell.%20In%20the%20USA%2C%0A%20%20at%20least%2C%20the%20Uniform%20Code%20Council%20does%20that.%20Once%20you%20have%20a%20number%20for%20your%0A%20%20product%2C%20feel%20free%20to%20come%20back%20here%20to%20look%20at%20the%20barcode%20associated%20with%0A%20%20that%20number%2C%20and%20save%20it%2C%20or%20print%20it%2C%20or%20what%20have%20you.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20The%20previous%20paragraph%20isn't%20enough%20for%20some%20people.%20Here%20is%0A%20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22use.html%22%3Ea%20more%20detailed%20explanation%3C%2Fa%3E.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3EThe%20Devil's%20In%20The%20Details...%3Ci%3ENot!%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20One%20thing%20that%20people%20like%20to%20ask%20a%20lot%20is%20what%20the%20%22meaning%22%20is%0A%20%20of%20the%20little%20marks%20to%20the%20left%20and%20right%20and%20smack%20dab%20in%20the%20middle%20of%0A%20%20the%20code.%20On%20either%20side%20is%20a%20pair%20of%20thin%20dark%20bars%20separated%20by%20a%20thin%0A%20%20light%20bar%2C%20and%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20